Quickstrike:









Quickstrike screamed and scurried to the side, in surprise from Trantsulas. 
He backed up and threw his good claw up in defense, but froze as he saw the 
spider.

"T?" he said to him. It looked like Tarantsulus was back from the dead. He 
was dumbfounded for a few seconds, then quickly mused over his aid. "Sure, 
sure, jus' get me outta here, b'fore ah's gets killed!" He crawled up to his 
side.
